title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-23-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-23-2014 THURS.......PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program





The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


     
The Glenn Beck Program - 1/23/14Thursday, January 23, 2014 11:17 AM






Lots covered on today's show, 

  like the how America used to do amazing things by amazing people,
    like Frank Sinatra.  

    Glenn uses lyrics from a Sinatra song that should dictate your life, 
         if you're brave enough to embrace them.

  Also, TX Senator Ted Cruz joins the show to discuss his thoughts
     on the current administrations faults and his run for office.

  Plus, the media reaction to Glenn's comments on Fox News the other night
         ...you'll be surprised.
